com.sun.jdo.spi.persistence.support.sqlstore.query.jqlc

Class CodeGeneration

  • java.lang.Object
    • antlr.TreeParser
      • com.sun.jdo.spi.persistence.support.sqlstore.query.jqlc.CodeGeneration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CodeGenerationTokenTypes

    public class CodeGeneration
extends antlr.TreeParser
implements CodeGenerationTokenTypes
    This class defines the code generation pass of the JQL compiler. Input of this pass is the typed and optimized AST as produced by optimizer. The result is a RetrieveDesc.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Michael Bouschen, Shing Wai Chan

      • candidateRD

        protected RetrieveDesc candidateRD
        The RetrieveDesc for the candidate class. Code gen for the CLASS_DEF AST will initilaized this variable. Code gen for the filter expression will add the constraints.

      • rd2TagMap

        protected Map rd2TagMap
        rd2TagMap maps RetrieveDesc to tags. A tag is either the variable name or the navigation path that used to create a new RetrieveDesc. This info is needed to identify whether two different RetrieveDescs denote the same variable or relationship.

      • boundRetrieveDescs

        protected Set boundRetrieveDescs
        Set of RetrieveDescs. CodeGeneration uses this set to prevent multiple addConstraint calls for the RetrieveDescs denoting a variable.

      • WILDCARD_PATTERN

        protected static final String WILDCARD_PATTERN
        Defines the SQL wildcard character to be used in wildcard pattern (string methods startsWith and endsWith).

      • getKeyFieldsComparisonBooleanOp

        protected int getKeyFieldsComparisonBooleanOp(int operation)
        Returns the boolean operation used to connect the key field comparison expressions: l == r is mapped to l.pk1 == r.pk1 & ... & l.pkn == r.pkn => return & l != r is mapped to l.pk1 != r.pk1 | ... | l.pkn != r.pkn => return |
